---

This approach ties your experience of her to something tangible and real, while also honoring the depth of your connection. It’s a way to express your truth without overwhelming her—it grounds the profound in something she can understand logically, while still capturing the magic of what you feel.

Now, after I told her what I am feeling, even these few minutes are silent, because now what I want to tell her cannot be told in 2 or 3 minutes. Nor can I have a small talk, how’s the weather, what did you have for launch. I can’t do that anymore. The things we have to discuss need time. And time with no distractions.
